    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner! If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great and feels even better on the road, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
