    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a wonderful example of pride in ownership, presenting in a striking Obsidian Black finish that still holds a deep, mirror-like shine. While there are a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with highway use, the body panels are straight and free of any significant dings. Inside, the Charcoal leather interior has been kept in a smoke-free environment; the seats are firm and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the heated power seats and the sunroof, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a comprehensive folder of receipts included. The most recent service included a synthetic oil change, new brake pads, and a fresh set of all-season tires. It starts up quietly, idles smoothly, and provides a composed, rattle-free ride. This is a dependable, well-documented car that bridges the gap between a daily driver and a collector's piece.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
